There is artwork of Din's crest to represent the Triforce of Power from the May 2023 Splatfest in Splatoon 3 to celebrate the release of The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom. The text is outlined in a pale pink glow and reads, "Team Power!"

The image on the left side is a golden crown with the Tumblr logo and the image on the left side is a blinking purple eye. Clicking on the blinkie leads to the source
